@startuml
title Request After Logout

actor User
participant "Blazor SSR Client" as Client
participant "OIDC Middleware" as Middleware
participant "Identity Provider" as IdP

User -> Client : GET /dispatcher
Client -> Middleware : No cookie

Middleware -> User : redirect /identity/login
User -> IdP : authenticate again

note right
Without IdP logout:
user would be logged in instantly (SSO cookie)
end note

@enduml
